data.description: Explore Atlanta's Hidden Gem - Pittsburgh! Discover the potential in Atlanta's most exciting emerging neighborhood with this charming brick duplex. Whether you're an investor seeking opportunity or a homeowner ready to make your mark, this property holds the key to your dreams.  Enter inside the fully renovated back unit, where luxury meets comfort. Revel in the beauty of LVP flooring, a new HVAC system, a tankless water heater, and a suite of stainless steel appliances, including a washer/dryer. The front unit, a canvas for your vision, awaits your personal touch to match the modern upgrades in the rear. Each 2-bed/1-bath unit opens up to a private fenced backyard, perfect for pets and hosting unforgettable gatherings.  Location? Unbeatable. You'll find yourself directly across from the Beltline's Pittsburgh Yards, granting you seamless access to the neighborhood's vibrant offerings – parks, restaurants, breweries, boutiques, and more. Your options are limitless: Capitalize on rental income from both units as Pittsburgh Yards continues to soar in value. Make the updated back unit your home and leisurely remodel the front to craft a sought-after rental property. Combine both units into a spacious haven for your growing family.   This is your chance to invest in Atlanta's future. Don't let it slip away. Picture the possibilities and seize this extraordinary opportunity. Schedule a showing today to secure your viewing now!
